i-MSCP Mailman plugin ChangeLog
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.3
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: 'mailman' list name must be disallowed

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: Entities with status set to 'disabled' must not be counted by the getItemWithErrorStatus() plugin method
	Fixed: IP addresses used in the Apache vhost files must match the IP addresses of the domains
	Fixed: IPv6 addresses in the Apache vhost file must be enclosed in square brackets
	Fixed: Wrong DNS resources record added when an IPv6 address is used

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Release: First released version
